{"type": "article", "id": 21607, "title": "manfred by francesco frulio&stefan lechner&samuele miatello", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-01T01:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606154039sBQh4MN5iGWv29pH.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>这张桌子的结构灵感来自第一架飞机的木结构机翼，贴近桌面有一排特别的承重结构，是由榉木胶合板做的。而桌面采用了磨砂水晶，可以看到桌子的结构，像是飞机旁边的一片云，也让这张桌子有轻盈的漂浮感。设计师想要以此达到“一种云朵消失不见的效果”。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154036XTYcZPMAbwsQey9F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154037i1nCozGyNrEW6xhM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154037RlW839mcvTEUrjCG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59535452\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154038XbkBIjt0HKhciW7M.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61858191\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154038wDyXAxQalpYKSndj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}